            "In the zoning plan, as far as special zonings are not determined, the significant conditions for spatial planning, like planned state- and federal highways, must be visualized."@en ;
        skos:inScheme <https://registry.inspire.gv.at/codelist/vbgLandUseValue> ;
        skos:notation "VSPE" ;
        skos:prefLabel "Verkehrsfläche Straße Planung Ersichtlichmachung"@de,
